Cinematographer and Project details:
(Photo attached of cast call) 

Hello everyone! 

Myself and another are co-producing a sci-fi short film and are looking for a cinematographer. 

The film follows the events leading up to beginning of an apocalyptic world. Where the people required to re-start society are trapped in a safe house. 

This is a small indie project, which is being self-funded, so this is an unpaid role, as the budget will be going towards locations, costuming, food, etc. However there is a possible opportunity to be given a room to stay overnight on set. 

The dates will be the 28th, 29th, 30th of November. 
The location is a little TBD but will be in the vicinity of Brisbane/GC (likely towards Brisbane). 

The genre: Sci-fi 
Estimated # of actors: 8 

There will be a variety of different skin tones, so needs to know how to light them accordingly without washing anyone out or darkening them. 

For any questions or if interested in the position please email  a.to.z.infinite.8@gmail.com

items.text:
Hey everyone! My name is Jackson Smith and I'm a fourth year at CU Boulder working on my BFA thesis film! I'm looking to fill two lead rolls if anyone is interested:

Title: Intersection

Genre: Drama

Logline: The film follows three people who unexpectedly effect each other while trying to make their way through a normal day. Introspective and character-focused. Very open to collaboration!

Roles: 

**Kat (Female, ~18-24)**: A young adult trying to find her footing. Kat often finds herself pushing forward in an attempt to forget what is behind her. She has a troubled relationship with her mother and has not been in contact with her for some time. It is now the day of her mother's birthday and Kat feels obligated to get her a cake.

**Heather (Female, 30s/40s)**: Kat's mother, independent and headstrong. Currently working as a freelance consultant, she really had to hustle to get to where she is now. However, her success came at the cost of her personal relationships. Heather wishes she and her daughter could reconnect, but she's not sure how to go about it. It is now Heather's birthday.

Production Type: Student

Contact Information: jasm4113@colorado.edu, (720)525-9544

Run Time: Short, ~12 minutes

Compensation: Unpaid (there will be food)

Union Status: Non-Union

Shooting Schedule: Rehearsal on Friday the 21st, shooting on the 22nd and 23rd of November

Filming Location: Boulder, Pearl Street

‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚ÄîCASTING CALL FOR **THE GREEN PASSPORT**‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî

We are students of Budapest Metropolitan University and currently in our 3rd year on Film and Media bachelors. For our Diploma Film we are looking for actors in 2 main roles. 

LOGLINE OF THE FILM:

In a midst of chaos caused by losing her passport on the first day of the visit, the mom and the son rediscover their long gone connection and love for each other. And the trip ends and they have to say goodbye when they finally reconnect with each other.

Below you can find the important infos about the characters:

CHARACTER‚ÄôS RACE
* South American
* South Asian

MARIA
* 50
* Nurse
* Overprotective, still distant
* Slightly closed minded
* Not expressive or vulnerable most of the time
* Caring but does not know how to 
* Kind
* Emotionally strong
* Ambitious
* From a working class family and saved up money to be in Europe
* Does not speak English well

ETHAN
* 20 - 27
* Lives in Europe
* Studies literature English
* Used to be sweet and naive but now more aware and mature
* Academically smart but not street smart 
* Gets overwhelmed easily 
* Anxious in stressful situations but manages to resolve them
* Expressive, shows emotions but not to the mum

ADDITIONAL INFO ABOUT THE PROJECT:
* This is a university film and our budget is very low, so this is an **UNPAID** work.
* The shooting most probably will happen in the 2nd part of April. 
* Before the shooting we will hold rehearsals (end March/ early April).
* The shooting will happen in the actors‚Äô native language, but the process of the shooting and the communication during the shoot will be English, so English language skills **REQUIRED**.

If you are interested please send us headshots and previous works of yourself to [thegreenpassport.work@gmail.com](mailto:thegreenpassport.work@gmail.com).

üé¨ CASTING CALL ‚Äì ‚ÄúEVIL GNOME‚Äù

In this campy slasher horror short, a young pair of dancers at an 80s tribute show sneak out (cheating on their partners) and are forced to face the consequences of their illicit actions. Trapped in a life or death game against a garden gnome possessed by an evil spirit , they must fight for their lives.

We‚Äôre casting for:
üßë‚Äçü¶± 1 Male Actor (19‚Äì25)
Role: Fabio a cocky, self-confident, dancer‚Ä¶ drug dealer and aspiring footballer but a coward underneath his roadman exterior. Must have a strong London/ MLE accent. Costume will be provided. Must be available all day Monday 17th November 

üìç Filming Location: Egham, Surrey
üé• Project: 6-minute short horror film 
üìÖ Shoot Date: Monday 17th November (11am‚Äì10pm)
üéûÔ∏è Self-tape or message Deadline: 11pm 15th November

If you‚Äôre passionate about fun, bold genre storytelling and love diving into energetic, expressive roles, we‚Äôd love to hear from you. This is an unpaid role for actors looking to gain experience or add to their portfolio.

üìß Please email arjanbains20@gmail.com for the audition pack, or send me a private message to learn more.

Please note this role is unpaid, but food and drink will be provided.

**Seeking Upright Bassist with Basic Acting Experience **

***Filming will be on 11/21 and 11/23***** **

***Copy, imbd credit, meal (it is a student film)***

**Location:** Los Angeles, CA (South Gate / Monterey Park / 

Pasadena)

**How to contact:** DM me here or email Rachel.lafcasting@gmail.com

**Story Synopsis, *****Blue Notes*****:**

Set in the smoky glow of late night jazz clubs, *Blue Notes* follows a young saxophonist whose life changes after meeting a woman who sees beyond the music. As his career takes off, he's caught between the thrill of the stage and the pull of something deeper.

‚Äî with Misha Edwards and Sam Jalalpour

**üé¨ CASTING CALL ‚Äì Background Actors Needed! üé¨**

We‚Äôre looking for **background actors** for our upcoming **independent feature film *****Express Entry*** shooting in **Surrey, BC**.

üìÖ **Dates & Requirements:**
* **Nov 29:** 6 background actors needed
* **Nov 30:** 4 background actors needed
* **Time:** Approx. 4 hours each day
* **Location:** Surrey, BC
* **Open to all genders and ethnicities**
* These are **different scenes on both days**, so we‚Äôre looking for **different people each day** (no repeats).

üé• **About the Project:**
This is a **volunteer position** ‚Äì perfect for anyone who wants to **gain experience on a film set**, be part of a **fun shoot**, and **network with passionate filmmakers**.

üç™ **Perks:**
* Crafty (snacks & refreshments) provided
* **IMDb credit**
* A great opportunity to see how an indie film set works!

If interested, please email your **name, photo, and availability** to **expressentryfilm@gmail.com** with the subject line **‚ÄúBackground Actor ‚Äì Express Entry.‚Äù**

Come join the team and be part of something special! üé•‚ú®

items.text:
Personal Short Film Project

SEEKING 2 ACTORS FOR MAIN CAST

WHEN: Dec 20‚Äì23, 2025

PAID: CAD $150 / Day

Project Title:

The Thought Experiment ‚ÄúMETA MONTAGE‚Äù

Genre:

Meta-psychological Drama / Experimental Metafiction / Postmodern Romance

Logline:

When a screenwriter finds himself inside the very film he‚Äôs writing, reality and fiction intertwine ‚Äî forcing him, his characters, and even the audience to confront the question: Who is truly creating whom?

A visual and interactive interpretation of the Multiverse Theory.

Production Details:

Dates: December 20‚Äì23, 2025

Location: Vancouver, BC

Rate: CAD $150 / day

Type: Independent Short Film (non-union, paid)

Casting:

JACK (30s)

An expressive man in his 30s. Starts as a victim tied to a chair but gradually becomes both the actor and writer of the film. Moves between fiction and reality, showing layers of vulnerability and control.

Keywords: Actor / Writer / Victim / Meta-role

Look: Half-dressed, sweaty, bloody ‚Üí later calm and casual.

NARRATOR (30s‚Äì40s)

A calm, mysterious man in a classic suit. Both inside and outside the film, he speaks directly to the camera as a philosophical observer. His emotions slowly break through his composed tone.

Keywords: Narrator / Observer / Director-like

Look: Formal, mustache, black & white lighting, under spotlight.

I‚Äôll be sending those who emailed me a 6-minute short film I recently shot, along with a script excerpt from the project.

I‚Äôd really appreciate it if you could send me a video of yourself reading the script by November 23

Hi everyone! I'm casting a **voice over commercial **for StatsCan, and we are looking for people (men and women, 25-75 years old) that can speak **Inuktitut. **These ads will run across TV, Web and Radio.

If you're interested in auditioning, please email me at: **adriennelindsaycasting@gmail.com** for details. I will send you the script of an ad we did a few years ago. To audition, you will need to record yourself reading the ad and send it in to me. We are looking for "official-sounding" reads.

**Specs**:

South Baffin (Inuktitut Nunavut) dialect.
*Talent can be based anywhere, but will need access to a professional recording studio to patch in.*

Usage: voice over commercial - multiple spots across TV, Web and Radio. Open to both ACTRA & non-union performers.

Thank you!

# **CASTING CALL FOR:**
# **ACTORS, VOICE ACTORS, SINGERS/VOCALISTS**
## 
# *' he lives here. '*

MANCHESTER BASED ONLY 

From writer/director/producer Jacob James Ward 

Watch my showreel here:

[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gIponbMURSU](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gIponbMURSU)

'he lives here.'

A sleepless corporate worker is forced to confront the monstrous embodiment of their childhood trauma during a terrifying sleep paralysis episode

A new gothic-noir, psychological thriller!

This project is deeply rooted in experimental film, with roles dominantly demanding body-performance with smaller amounts of spoken dialogue. 

This could be a good fit for those looking to get into experimental film with interests in deep character development/immersion within the horror/thriller genres! 

CASTING FOR 2 MAIN ROLES, VOICE ACTORS & VOCALISTS

BENNY

Male presenting, playing age 20-30

Benny, a reclusive loner caught between a draining job and worsening sleep paralysis partially due to unresolved trauma from his estranged father, battles his paranoia in an empty house

THE FIGURE 

Male presenting, playing age 20-30 

A manifestation of his deepest fears, the figure appears to Benny one evening in frightening hallucinations

VOICE ACTORS

Any age, but with a focus on more mature voices (40+) 

VOCALIST

To help in making the score of the film. Feminine-leaning vocals rooted in dreamy soundscapes and soft spoken word. Inspo: Phoebe Bridgers, Agnes Obel, Ethel Cain

Filming on dates in December (depending on actor availability) 

UNPAID STUDENT FILM 

MANCHESTER BASED ONLY 

Please reach out via this Facebook page or email at jacobward044@gmail.com 

to express interest and find out more info!

Much love 

X

Casting Call for Short 10-15 minutes called Repossession 

This is a  darkly comic short about ambition, fame, and the unexpected horrors lurking behind a routine job.

Casting call for the characters 
Kyle
 A seasoned presenter clinging to relevance in a changing media landscape. Desperate for a comeback, he takes one last job‚Äîblinded by ambition, even when the warning signs turn supernatural.
 Playing Age: Early 30s to mid 40s
 Ethnicity: Any
 Gender: Male
Spencer
 Kyle‚Äôs loyal second-in-command, tasked with shaping the show‚Äôs content. Often dragged into eerie locations, Spencer must confront whether he‚Äôs valued as a partner‚Äîor just a pawn.
 Playing Age: Mid 20s to Mid 30s
 Ethnicity: Any
 Gender: Male
Carla Curses
 A flashy social media psychic with a massive following and a hunger for viral fame. Her pursuit of a haunted object leads to possession‚Äîtransforming her into something savage and inhuman.
 Playing Age: 20s to 30s
 Ethnicity: Any
 Gender: Female
Frank
Carla‚Äôs trusted cameraman, now shattered by the night‚Äôs horrors. Haunted and fragile, his trauma slowly pulls him into the house‚Äôs darkness.
Playing Age: 30s to 40s
Ethnicity: Any
Physicality: Tall and lanky
Gender: Male

Filming will take place in the Liverpool/Merseyside area, United Kingdom. Looking to film middle to end of January 2026 
Please apply only if you're based locally.
For more details, contact: houndsoftheroundtable@gmail.com

Please note we do not reply to comments or direct Facebook messages. Thank you!

üåç **You're Invited: Alex Fil's 27th Birthday Bash in Covent Garden ‚Äì I'm Alone in the UK & Need Your Company! üéÇ‚ú®**

Hey London (and world wanderers)! I'm Alex Fil ‚Äì Ukrainian TV presenter living my London adventure **but completely alone here, with no one to celebrate my birthday with**. Turning 27 on **28 November at 7:30 PM** ‚Äì join me for an open, fun-filled evening at **Apple Market, Covent Garden (WC2E 8RF)**!

I'll bring some cake & drinks to share, but since **I have no friends or family nearby** (and don't know who's coming!), bring your faves: snacks, bubbly, balloons, or just your amazing self. Let's turn my lonely day into a pop-up party under the market lights ‚Äì good vibes, stories, and maybe a spontaneous sing-along? üòä

**RSVP: Comment below or DM me!** Tag friends who can make a stranger's day. #CoventGardenParty #LondonBirthdayBash #AloneInUK #BringYourVibes

Vor einigen Tagen habe ich im Netz einige Beitr√§ge gesehen von Menschen auf der Stra√üe. Sie wurden interviewt,  sind nach Herkunft, Perspektiven und mehr weiter gefragt worden. Das hat mich sehr aufgew√ºhlt. Heute nach einer langen Studio Session habe ich mich gefragt warum ich so einen Song geschrieben habe? 
Mit‚ÄúHINTER DEN BERGEN‚Äú ist ein neues Werk f√ºr das Projekt SONNENFEUER entstanden.

We‚Äôre excited to announce casting for BROCCOLI LAW, a comedic short student film produced through Toronto Metropolitan University, shooting in the Toronto/GTA area this February.

The film follows an eight-year-old boy facing ‚Äúarrest‚Äù for refusing to eat his vegetables ‚Äî a playful, deadpan world filled with sharp humour, eccentric adults, and dynamic roles for both young performers and character actors.

We are seeking Union and Non-Union talent. These roles are unpaid. 

All role descriptions are included in the attached images.

Casting submissions are due ASAP. Submit headshot, demo reel, and CV to broccolilawfilm@gmail.com

We can‚Äôt wait to see your auditions!

***CASTING FOR NATIVITY! THE MUSICAL***

Looking for musical theatre performers who are not doing panto but would still love to do a show this Christmas!!

We are producing a charity production of NATIVITY! THE MUSICAL here in Romford

We are looking for....

GORDON SHAKESPEARE (Male - playing age 30-45) Hugely competitive teacher at Oakmoor Prep School. Bari/Tenor vocals

LORD MAYOR / ENSEMBLE (Male - playing age 35-60)

MISS RYE / ENSEMBLE (Female - playing age 23-50)

THE CRITIC / ENSEMBLE (Any Gender - playing age 25-60)

HOLLYWOOD PRODUCER / ENSEMBLE (Any Gender - playing age 25-60)

Show runs 4-23 Dec 2025

Venue: Brookside Theatre Romford

Production: Charity musical

Rehearsals: Monday - Thursday daytimes / evenings by schedule

Remuneration: Flat Fee

Please PM for more info or email harri@brooksidetheatre.com

Looking for FEMALE and MALE dancers for an upcoming festive contract in Dubai (UAE).

Also looking for event/costume assistants if anyone is interested or has contacts in this too. Thank you! 

**Details: **
* Contract dates - 29th Nov - 12 Jan in Dubai (UAE) - working days TBC (likely to be around 3-4 days per week). Potential to start earlier too (asap). 
* Location: Dubai (UAE) 
* Contract type: Festive choreographed dance shows, more details will be shared in due course to those who are interested 
* Flights (not covered)
* Accommodation - if needed can potentially help with this 
* Salary - full salary will be disclosed in due course to interested applicants - it will be over ¬£2000 

**To apply: **
1. Please email hello.showcreation@gmail.com asap (ideally by the 19th Nov) with your...
2. CV 
3. Photos
4. Dance showreel - if you have any tricks (acro, partner acro, breaking etc.) or special skills please share them too 

**Additional skills: **
1. If you also have presenting skills or are confident with the microphone/engaging guests please share this material too 
2. If you have any experience of or are interested in show production, especially costume production/sourcing, please mention this in your application 

Thank you so much!

**Raum Rheinland | Freundinnen-Paar zum Thema Geschenke f√ºr TV-Beitrag gesucht**

** **

F√ºr einen TV-Beitrag des Magazins ‚ÄûLife‚Äú suchen wir zwei Freundinnen, die im Rheinland zuhause sind. Gemeinsam mit euch wollen wir testen, welche Methode das beste Geschenk f√ºr die Person an eurer Seite hervorbringt: eure eigene Idee, die Empfehlung einer Expertin oder der Vorschlag einer KI.

 

Im Experiment √ºberlegt ihr euch zun√§chst jeweils ein Geschenk f√ºreinander. Danach besprecht ihr eure Ideen mit einer Expertin, die ebenfalls ein Geschenk f√ºr die andere Person entwickelt. Zum Abschluss tritt eine KI an ‚Äì und wir schauen, welches Geschenk am Ende am meisten √ºberzeugt.

 

Ihr habt Lust mitzumachen und herauszufinden, womit ihr der anderen Person die gr√∂√üte Freude machen k√∂nnt? Dann schreibt mir einfach eine Nachricht :)

Freue mich auf eure Nachrichten!

items.text:
**UL√òNNET**

Vi er et hold fra Potemkin, Den Jyske Filmskole, der er i gang med vores afgangsprojekt

Vi s√∏ger en mand i spillealderen 18-23 til hovedrollen Milo

Kort om historien:
En ung mand med et spiralerende heroinmisbrug vender hjem til sin syge mor for f√∏rste gang i m√•nedsvis. Han kommer for at bede om penge - men ender som et stille opg√∏r mellem k√¶rlighed og skam. Vi √∏nsker ikke at lave en film som glorificerer stoffer, men om, hvordan det nedbryder de st√¶rkeste relationer mellem mennesker.

Om rollen:
Milo er 23 og fanget i sit eget forfald. Bag afh√¶ngigheden gemmer sig en s√∏n, der stadig elsker sin mor, men ikke l√¶ngere kan b√¶re at blive set af hende. Skylden, k√¶rligheden og skammen eksisterer side om side i ham.
Rollen kr√¶ver en skuespiller med evnen til at udtrykke mere gennem stilhed end gennem ord - en fysisk og f√∏lelsesm√¶ssig tilstedev√¶relse, hvor sm√• reaktioner og blikke fort√¶ller alt.

Praktisk:
Optagelserne finder sted i Aarhus den 24. og 25. november.
Der vil v√¶re fuld forplejning p√• settet, men vi vil ikke kunne betale k√∏n, transport eller overnatning.

Hvis du er interesseret i at blive taget i betragtning til rollen, bedes du indsende et kort selftape af dummy teksten, der er vedh√¶ftet i opslaget. Send det meget gerne til mailen nedenfor.

Vi h√•ber, at projektet v√¶kker din nysgerrighed - og at du har lyst til at tage del i fort√¶llingen om Milo og hans mor.

Med venlig hilsen

Team ‚ÄúI Limbo‚Äù
Bastian Kapela
Producer, Potemkin ‚Äì Den Jyske Potemkin Filmskole

bastiankapela@gmail.com

## **CASTING CALL ‚Äì ‚ÄúTale of Two‚Äù (Short Film)**

**Logline:**
*‚ÄúTale of Two‚Äù* is a portrait short film about women‚Äôs strength, focusing on our shared experiences rather than our differences. Through small, intimate scenes, we witness key moments in the lives of two women as they navigate hardship, love, and resilience in parallel journeys.

**Production Details:**
* **Location:** Downtown Vancouver
* **Shoot Dates:** 1-3 days ‚Äì end of January
* **Format:** MOS (no sync sound) ‚Äì performances will rely heavily on expressive, facial acting
* **Union Status:** Non-Union / Volunteer Passion Project
* **Compensation:** Volunteer basis with **great meals, greater company, and IMDb credit**.
Select roles (requiring multiple full days) will receive a **small honorarium**.

**To Submit:**
Please send your **headshot and CV/demo reel**, which **role** you‚Äôre applying for and a **self-tape** with the attached actions **taleoftwofilm@gmail.com**.
Include a **slate** with your **name, age, height,** and any **unavailable dates**.
**Submission Deadline:** *November 25th at midnight.*

Casting Call!

*Starchild* is a sci-fi drama that follows the story of two scientists, Vanessa and Tanner as they take separate paths to deal with their grief. Vanessa through faith, and Tanner through science. It's not until they discover the origins of life itself, that they reconcile to start a family of their own. 

The film is heartfelt, honest, and powerful.

Please send resume, headshot, and (if applicable) demo reel to starchildcasting@gmail.com

üö® CASTING CALL ‚Äì FEATURE FILM üö® (RDE FILMS)

RDE Films is now accepting auditions for our upcoming feature film. We‚Äôre seeking bold, authentic performers with strong presence and emotional range. Following directions is extremely important to our process.

‚∏ª

AVAILABLE ROLES

Detective 1 ‚Äì Male, 25‚Äì35

Types: Jon Bernthal, Shia LaBeouf, Denzel Washington, Lakeith Stanfield, Benjamin Bratt.
Barrio-raised energy. (Willing to smoke fake herbal cigarettes.)

Types: Lakeith Stanfield, Michael B. Jordan, Don Cheadle.

Assistant District Attorney ‚Äì Male, 25‚Äì45
Strong personality, ‚Äúboss energy,‚Äù sharp and commanding. The quintessential lawyer type.

Killer ‚Äì Male, 30‚Äì45
Soft-spoken, intelligent, creepy, and quietly imposing.
Think Ed Gein, Arthur Fleck, Longlegs.

Racist Pastor ‚Äì Male, 35‚Äì55
Charismatic, silver-tongued, sly, and playful ‚Äî hides malice behind a smile.

Killer‚Äôs Mother ‚Äì Female, 40‚Äì60
Quiet, submissive, battered southern housewife. Soft-spoken and broken.

Killer‚Äôs Father ‚Äì Male, 40‚Äì60
Abusive, mean, southern personality. Stoic, intimidating, and abrasive.

Captain of Precinct ‚Äì Male, 35‚Äì65
Respectable, strong leader type. Endearing and commanding presence.

Missing Child ‚Äì Female, 10‚Äì13 
Smart, articulate, emotionally mature. Must be able to cry and portray broken emotion.

Missing Child‚Äôs Mother ‚Äì Female, 25‚Äì35
Loving, playful, fiery. Must portray grief, depression, and distraught emotion.

Angry Mother (Smoker Mom) ‚Äì Female, 25‚Äì35
Mean, vindictive, narcissistic with a bad attitude. (Willing to smoke fake herbal cigarettes.) Think of the mother from the movie ‚ÄúPrecious.‚Äù

Gang Leader ‚Äì Male, 30‚Äì40 (Latinx Preference)
Calm but powerful demeanor. Ex-convict type with commanding presence.
Ability to perform a Chicano accent required.

items.text:
Hi! 

I‚Äôm currently casting a well paid shoot for an alcohol brand

As it‚Äôs advertising for alcohol all cast legally need to be at least 25 (production will ask for id to prove this if shortlisted by client) however the concept for the project is quite youthful so max age should be 30. 

Casting Brief: 

Looking for European girls with coloured hair (think red, blue, pink, green, berry, purple) or happy to have their hair coloured for the shoot. 

Looking for European boys with facial hair (a moustache and/or beard - bonus if you have an interesting hair cut too) 

This is a London shoot so looking for London based people only. 

**Shoot Dates: **Thursday 27th + Friday 28th November

Talent to attend both shoot days in London on Location

Based on a 10 hour shoot day including an additional hour for lunch

**Fitting Date:** Monday 24th November, 1-2 hours in London (between 9am and 6pm)

**Talent Age: **All Talent to be over 25 and passport or ID needs to be provided at the time of shortlist to confirm this 

**Talent Rates:**

Talent Day Rates - ¬£600 per person per day

Talent Usage* ¬£5,000 per model

*Usage not guaranteed however all talent are shot in groups so this is very likely to be confirmed

**Talent Wardrobe:**

Talent will be required to bring a couple of outfits to the shoot which will be briefed by the wardrobe stylist

and either brought to the fitting or photographed before the shoot.

Hi! 

I‚Äôm currently casting a well paid shoot for an alcohol brand

As it‚Äôs advertising for alcohol all cast legally need to be at least 25 (production will ask for id to prove this if shortlisted by client) however the concept for the project is quite youthful so max age should be 30. 

Casting Brief: 

Looking for European girls with coloured hair (think red, blue, pink, green, berry, purple) or happy to have their hair coloured for the shoot. 

Looking for European boys with facial hair (a moustache and/or beard - bonus if you have an interesting hair cut too) 

This is a London shoot so looking for London based people only. 

**Shoot Dates: **Thursday 27th + Friday 28th November

Talent to attend both shoot days in London on Location

Based on a 10 hour shoot day including an additional hour for lunch

**Fitting Date:** Monday 24th November, 1-2 hours in London (between 9am and 6pm)

**Talent Age: **All Talent to be over 25 and passport or ID needs to be provided at the time of shortlist to confirm this 

**Talent Rates:**

Talent Day Rates - ¬£600 per person per day

Talent Usage* ¬£5,000 per model

*Usage not guaranteed however all talent are shot in groups so this is very likely to be confirmed

Talent will be required to bring a couple of outfits to the shoot which will be briefed by the wardrobe stylist

and either brought to the fitting or photographed before the shoot.

# **üéÑElf Work at Hertfordshire Zoo!üéÑ**

Hertfordshire Zoo is looking for jolly, enthusiastic, and festive individuals to bring the magic of Christmas to life this year at **Hertfordshire Zoo in Broxbourne, Hertfordshire.**

**What We‚Äôre Looking For:**
* A warm, friendly personality with plenty of festive spirit
* Confidence interacting with children and families
* Reliability and professionalism
* Previous performance or grotto experience (preferred but not essential)
* We have a mixture of performance elf and grotto elf work available

**When You‚Äôll Work:**

The dates we are currently still looking for people are:
* 26th November (4:30pm-8:30pm)
* 29th November (9:30am-4:00pm)
* 30th November (9:00am-5:00pm)
* 6th December (9:00am-5:00pm)
* 7th December (9:00am-5:00pm)
* 13th December (9:00am-5:00pm)
* 24th December (9:00am-3:00pm)

**PLEASE NOTE** - You are not required to be available to work on all of these dates. Any availability is accepted.

**What We Offer:**
* A fun and rewarding role in a magical setting
* ¬£14 per hour
* Full costume and training provided
* The chance to work at one of Hertfordshire's most loved attractions

If you would love to make Christmas unforgettable for our visitors, we‚Äôd love to hear from you.

Apply now by emailing **[entertainment@hertfordshirezoo.com](mailto:entertainment@hertfordshirezoo.com)**

items.text:
Today I will be EXPOSING a group of individuals that deserve nothing less than to be made accountable for their actions. STEALING IS NOT OK, USING STOLEN EQUIPMENT WITHOUT PAYING FOR IT, IS NOT OK.

STEALING a performer's equipment is literally like taking everything away from him because we all know in our line of work as entertainers we only depend on our skills and more importantly our equipment to survive and feed our families. 

Tuffy Nicholas, the owner of
"SUPER AMERICAN CIRCUS" in collaboration with his partner "DERRICK MUNA-QUINATA" Owner of "IEG"  are currently using assets to run their show that legally belong to me in their pirate show called "PIRATES OF THE PACIFIC" at the "PACIFIC ISLAND CLUB" in GUAM. 

They continue to operate their business with STOLEN CIRCUS EQUIPMENT worth $13,940.04 that rightfully belongs to me, this shameless behavior needs to be exposed in hopes that they pay me for it and that this never happens again. 

STEALING, a human beings possessions in which he depends on to make a living is a crime. After they first took it out of my container without my permission or consent they claimed they wanted to buy it which was totally wrong to begin with, then they didn't want to even pay for it , then Derrick MUNA-QUINATA owner of "IEG" wanted to send my equipment back to me without any insurance or pictures of the equipment he was sending back to me, which quite frankly to anybody this is scary because for one they should have never taken this equipment out without my consent and second if they actually wanted to send it back to me they should've absolutely ensured the equipment for its actual value of $13,940.04 instead of just trying to send it without any insurance which makes no sense because if the equipment "Broke" got "Damaged" or "all of it" didn't make it, they wouldn't be responsible.  Bottom line is they stole it and didn't pay for it and are now using my equipment to profit from it. 

While "TUFFY NICHOLAS" and "DERRICK MUNA-QUINATA" continue to make money of my stolen equipment I have suffered irreparable damages to my life and lost several contracts that I am still struggling to recover to this very day, even after simply asking them to pay for the equipment that was stolen from me, they never bothered to reply and why should they honestly. This type of human beings feel invincible because this is normal to them, they do not care or even consider the harm they continue to do unto others because nobody does anything about it. 

For this reason I have decided that it is time to EXPOSE "TUFFY NICHOLAS"  owner of the "SUPER AMERICAN CIRCUS" and "DERRICK MUNA-QUINATA" owner of "IEG" so that anyone that chooses to work with this companies, can be aware of what they can expect. 

These types of delinquencies happen way too often in our beautiful industry and they shouldn't, there's lots of beautiful human souls out there giving nothing but love and hard work, leaving behind their homes, their families and everything they love most with the promise of a better future and companies like "SUPER AMERICAN CIRCUS" and "IEG" are taking advantage of our beautiful industry, and it's not right.

I can't believe that after I tried reaching out to the owner of SUPER AMERICAN CIRCUS Tuffy Nicholas he didn't even bother to reply or show any concern which tells me he was well aware of my equipment being used in his company because if you're being accused of using stolen equipment anybody who's innocent or a decent human being for that matter would've responded immediately to such allegations, but this was not the case. 

ENOUGH IS ENOUGH.

Seriously, beware of these people and their companies because they will make you believe that you will have the best experience in your life while you are just trying to build a better future for you and your family working for them. However you will soon find out how shitty they truly are at giving a damn about your feelings.

I have all the original receipts and serial numbers for proof.

Thank you for reading.

STEALING, a human beings possessions in which he depends on to make a living is a crime. After they first took it out of my container without my permission or consent they claimed they wanted to buy it which was totally wrong to begin with, then they didn't want to even pay for it , then Derrick MUNA-QUINATA owner of "IEG" wanted to send my equipment back to me without any insurance or pictures of the equipment he was sending back to me, which quite frankly to anybody this is scary because for one they should have never taken this equipment out without my consent and second if they actually wanted to send it back to me they should've absolutely ensured the equipment for its actual value of $13,940.04 instead of just trying to send it without any insurance which makes no sense because if the equipment "Broke" got "Damaged" or "all of it" didn't make it, they wouldn't be responsible.  Bottom line is they stole it and didn't pay for it and are now using my equipment to profit from it. 

While "TUFFY NICHOLAS" and "DERRICK MUNA-QUINATA" continue to make money of my stolen equipment I have suffered irreparable damages to my life and lost several contracts that I am still struggling to recover to this very day, even after simply asking them to pay for the equipment that was stolen from me, they never bothered to reply and why should they honestly. This type of human beings feel invincible because this is normal to them, they do not care or even consider the harm they continue to do unto others because nobody does anything about it. 

For this reason I have decided that it is time to EXPOSE "TUFFY NICHOLAS"  owner of the "SUPER AMERICAN CIRCUS" and "DERRICK MUNA-QUINATA" owner of "IEG" so that anyone that chooses to work with this companies, can be aware of what they can expect. 

These types of delinquencies happen way too often in our beautiful industry and they shouldn't, there's lots of beautiful human souls out there giving nothing but love and hard work, leaving behind their homes, their families and everything they love most with the promise of a better future and companies like "SUPER AMERICAN CIRCUS" and "IEG" are taking advantage of our beautiful industry, and it's not right.

I can't believe that after I tried reaching out to the owner of SUPER AMERICAN CIRCUS Tuffy Nicholas he didn't even bother to reply or show any concern which tells me he was well aware of my equipment being used in his company because if you're being accused of using stolen equipment anybody who's innocent or a decent human being for that matter would've responded immediately to such allegations, but this was not the case. 

ENOUGH IS ENOUGH.

Seriously, beware of these people and their companies because they will make you believe that you will have the best experience in your life while you are just trying to build a better future for you and your family working for them. However you will soon find out how shitty they truly are at giving a damn about your feelings.

I have all the original receipts and serial numbers for proof.

Thank you for reading.

Die Vorbereitungen laufen weiter auf Hochtouren. Unser Projekt steht inzwischen auf einem stabilen Fundament, und die Crew w√§chst von Tag zu Tag. Jetzt beginnt die Phase, in der wir die passenden Schauspieler an Bord holen ‚Äì aber klar ist auch: Ein Film dieser Gr√∂√üe braucht weit mehr als nur ein starkes Ensemble.

F√ºr Viper ‚Äì Code Red haben wir die wichtigsten Bereiche definiert, die wir noch besetzen oder verst√§rken:

Aufnahmeleitung, Art Department, Beleuchtung, Budget/Finanzierung, Setbau, Casting, Catering, Camera Crew, Drehbuchunterst√ºtzung, Drehplanung, Drohnencrew, technisches Equipment, Schnitt/Editing, Fahrerteam und Transport, Ton/Sounddepartment, Grafik/Marketing, Herstellungsleitung, Hair & Make-Up, Intimit√§tskoordination (falls notwendig), Kameraabteilung, Kost√ºm, Komparsenmanagement, Locations/Motivbetreuung, Musik/Score, Produktionsb√ºro/Organisation, Produzenten/Produktionsleitung, Postproduktion inklusive VFX und Color Grading, Qualit√§tssicherung/Script Supervising, Regieassistenz, Requisiten, Waffenmeister, SFX, Stunts und Sicherheitsfachkr√§fte, Tonstudio/Mischung, Unit Management/Logistik, Distribution/Verleih, Werbung/Trailerproduktion sowie Zielgruppen-Analyse.

Ein wichtiger Punkt, auf den wir besonders stolz sind:

Viper ‚Äì Code Red ist offiziell bei IMDb gelistet.

Hier der Eintrag:

https://www.imdb.com/title/tt38784411/

Und jetzt der Teil, der f√ºr viele spannend ist:

Wir √∂ffnen erneut die Bewerbungsphase f√ºr Schauspieler, Nebenrollen und Kleinstrollen.

Wir suchen Menschen mit Pr√§senz, Energie und Charakter ‚Äì egal ob mit Erfahrung oder Neueinsteiger, solange die Haltung passt. Bewerbungen sind ausdr√ºcklich wieder m√∂glich.

Dazu kommt:

Wir suchen ebenso weitere Fachkr√§fte im Bereich Requisiten, Waffen, Spezialeffekte und technische Ausstattung.

Egal ob Props-Designer, Waffenmeister, SFX-Erfahrene oder Fachleute f√ºr realistische Einsatz- und Polizeiausr√ºstung ‚Äì hier gibt es viel Raum f√ºr Profis, die Lust auf ein ernstes Projekt haben.

Gerade deshalb ist diese Phase entscheidend:

Wir positionieren uns nicht als Fanprojekt, sondern als ernstes Filmvorhaben mit klarer Struktur, professionellen Bereichen und verl√§sslichen Prozessen. Jeder, der jetzt zu uns kommt, steigt in ein Projekt ein, das nach Standards arbeitet ‚Äì nicht nach Zufall.

Parallel beginnt die Besetzung unseres Schauspiel-Ensembles: Hauptrollen, Nebenrollen, wiederkehrende Figuren sowie das komplette Phoenix-Universum rund um Phoenix One, Phoenix Two und das Phoenix HQ. Jede Rolle erh√§lt Profil, Pr√§senz und Pers√∂nlichkeit ‚Äì und wir suchen Darsteller, die genau das mitbringen: Charakter, Haltung, Ausdauer und Lust auf eine realistische, bodenst√§ndige, kraftvolle Actionwelt.

Der Cast-Aufbau l√§uft.

Die Crew w√§chst.

Die Struktur steht.

Jetzt holen wir die Menschen dazu, die Viper ‚Äì Code Red lebendig machen.

Weitere Casting-Infos folgen.

It‚Äôs a wrap! Six Commercials with 50 Actors from MA to TX to RI and back to RI for 3 more this week!!  4 Picture cars in TX - RI!! Locations in RI!  

On Set Wrangler, Child Welfare Worker and Production Assistant!  

Catering and Crafty for 4 days! 

I have a new business: ACTORDASH - I don‚Äôt just cast ‚Äòem! I deliver them to set!

I jumped in feet first starting in August 2025, and although we still have some administrative work to do; we are officially wrapped!

I am now on Holiday Break and will be gearing up for more filming in January 2026!

During this break I will be doing a massive Talent Scout starting in Rhode Island!

I know I can easily find everyone I need for our Massachusetts needs with a simple post! But, I‚Äôve found it harder to find Actors in Rhode Island.

I am also planning a Karaoke Holiday Party for the first time since before Covid!  If you‚Äôd like to attend send an email to:

JodiPurdyCasting@gmail.com
Subj:  Holiday Party 2025

On another good note - my client is looking into signing a SAG Contract in 2026!  

But for the time being I will be casting Non-Union Actors and Real People to portray Doctors, Nurses, Medical Personnel and Patients from all walks of life living in Rhode Island.

Submit to:

JodiPurdyCasting@gmail.com
Subj: RI Resident NU Actor Real Person

items.text:
Hello everyone! 

Myself and another are co-producing a sci-fi short film and are looking for a cinematographer. 

The film follows the events leading up to beginning of an apocalyptic world. Where the people required to re-start society are trapped in a safe house. 

This is a small indie project, which is being self-funded, so this is an unpaid role, as the budget will be going towards locations, costuming, food, etc. However there is a possible opportunity to be given a room to stay overnight on set. 

The dates will be the 28th, 29th, 30th of November. 
The location is a little TBD but will be in the vicinity of Brisbane/GC (likely towards Brisbane). 

The genre: Sci-fi 
Estimated # of actors: 8 

There will be a variety of different skin tones, so needs to know how to light them accordingly without washing anyone out or darkening them. 

For any questions or if interested in the position please email  a.to.z.infinite.8@gmail.com

items.text:
CASTING CALL FOR NEW PLAY!
--------------------------------

A New Comedic play by Zack Faulks, *Bulimia is My Roman Empire* follows a group of Servants as they attempt to assassinate the Emperor. They discover that power may not be all that they had once desired. Learning that their target is engaged in a number of self-destructive behaviours, our conspirators are forced to follow down a long rabbit hole of strange diets, machismo, and fascism should they want to prove that they deserve the right to rule. As a satire of manhood, ultimately no one‚Äôs happy with where they end up.

For more information check out the images below!

Deadline to submit is Nov. 29, 2025 at 12:00pm.

--------------------
Find us at www.greattrashproductions.ca

items.text:
Casting Call (Non-Union) for COUPLES - Paid

Looking for actors to play the role of clients in a simulated therapy session. The video clips will be used in an online training system for counselors and psychologists. The sessions include some scripted elements to prepare, and then some improv with prompts.

We are currently interested in filming with mature couples, queer couples, interracial couples, or throuples/polycules of various gender identity combinations. All ages, all gender expressions/identities, all ethnicities, and persons with disabilities are welcome. 

All experience levels with acting are welcome, including experienced actors with less experienced partners. We are committed to making this a respectful and safe process, with open communication and respect for boundaries.

Comfortable English fluency is required.

Immediate filming dates are November 14 to 18, based on actor availability, but more will occur in the future so please submit if you're interested at all.

Location is downtown Vancouver - Gastown. Pay is $90 CAD per performer, with the expectation of some prepared material, studio session duration: 1 hour

Please email phil@skillsetter.com with your headshot and resume, as well as some information about you and your partner, such as gender identities, age, cultural/racial backgrounds. If you've submitted for a past session, you're welcome to submit again. We do sometimes receive more submissions than we are able to respond to, but we do read them all, and we do save your submissions for future consideration.

Still time to apply for our open casting for Spring Awakening! 

Off Topic are looking for creatives to join us in our new production of Frank Wedekind‚Äôs raw and revolutionary classic!
